        "body": "## What\r\n\r\nAdds missing `CHANGELOG.md` at repository root following Keep a Changelog format.\r\n\r\nIncludes:\r\n- Empty [Unreleased] section\r\n- Initial [0.1.0] release section with current workspace and CI setup\r\n\r\n\r\n## Why\r\n\r\n`CHANGELOG.md` is referenced in CONTRIBUTING.md but was missing, blocking the PR checklist and release tracking.\r\n\r\n\r\n## How\r\n\r\n- Created CHANGELOG.md at root\r\n- Followed Keep a Changelog structure\r\n- Added initial 0.1.0 release based on existing crates and infrastructure\r\n\r\n\r\n## Checklist\r\n\r\n- [x] CHANGELOG.md added and properly formatted\r\n\n\n<!-- This is an auto-generated comment: release notes by coderabbit.ai -->\n## Summary by CodeRabbit\n\n* **Documentation**\n  * Added a changelog (Keep-a-Changelog + SemVer) with an Unreleased section and a 0.1.0 entry; clarified that boolean-mask indexing returns a copy.\n\n* **New Features**\n  * Publicly exposed indexing modules, masked-array I/O, runtime SIMD detection, and the ufunc surface.\n\n* **Examples**\n  * Improved example output formatting across multiple crates for clearer, multi-line displays.\n\n<!-- review_stack_entry_start -->\n\n[![Review Change Stack](https://storage.googleapis.com/coderabbit_public_assets/review-stack-in-coderabbit-ui.svg)](https://app.coderabbit.ai/change-stack/mohu-org/mohu/pull/199?utm_source=github_walkthrough&utm_medium=github&utm_campaign=change_stack)\n\n<!-- review_stack_entry_end -->\n<!-- end of auto-generated comment: release notes by coderabbit.ai -->",
