        "body": "## Description\r\n\r\nFixes #323\r\n\r\nAdds JSDoc documentation and examples for time utility functions.\r\n\r\n- Added JSDoc for getSecondsUntilUTCMidnight\r\n- Added JSDoc for getSecondsUntilMidnightInTimezone\r\n- Included @example usage\r\n- Documented DST edge cases\r\n- No logic changes (refactor only)\r\n\r\n## Pillar\r\n\r\n- [ ] 🎨 Pillar 1 — New Theme Design\r\n- [ ] 📐 Pillar 2 — Geometric SVG Improvement\r\n- [ ] 🕐 Pillar 3 — Timezone Logic Optimization\r\n- [x] 🛠️ Other (Bug fix, refactoring, docs)\r\n\r\n## Visual Preview\r\n\r\nN/A\r\n\r\n## Checklist before requesting a review:\r\n\r\n- [x] I have read the `CONTRIBUTING.md` file.\r\n- [x] I have tested these changes locally.\r\n- [x] My commits follow the Conventional Commits format.\r\n- [ ] I have updated README.md if needed.\r\n- [x] I have made sure that I have only one commit in this PR.",
